  "title": "Field value for cssClasses Item",
  "body": "Hi! I have a documentation issue on InstantSearch.js. I could not find what I was looking for on the page \"[refinementList](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/refinementList.html)\".\r\n\r\n<!-- Describe what you're looking for here. -->\r\n\r\nIs it possible to get the field value and assign this to the \"item\" cssClasses?\r\n\r\nSo for example;\r\n cssClasses: {\r\n      list: 'nav nav-list',\r\n      count: 'badge pull-right',\r\n      active: 'active',\r\n      item: {{field value}}\r\n    }\r\n\r\nThanks.",
